You are correct in your summation. This does indeed work. Very well in fact.

The only thing i can think of that he may be talking about is that maybe the initial "full game" releases of this game are screwed up and/or have non-working DLC. I've never had a problem with the Vansik Repack version i use but only one of the DLC's ever worked, even after the 1.7 update. It was only after i installed this DLC set that i finally got the other DLC's to work *at all* other than the Just Cause outfit. IDK though, all i can say is that this DLC set and crack does indeed work.
